## Optional Third (if you want to stand out more)

### RPC Framework (mini gRPC)

**Why this matters:**
Modern backend = microservices → communication matters.

**Core idea:**

* Define service → call function remotely

**What it shows:**

> “I understand how services talk in real systems.”

